<!DOCTYPE html>
{% set theme = app.user ? app.user.theme : app.session.get('theme', 'light') %}
<html lang="{{ app.request.locale|default('fr') }}" data-bs-theme="{{ theme }}">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{% block title %}Bouffay{% endblock %}</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 100 100%22><text y=%22.9em%22 font-size=%2290%22>🛍️</text></svg>">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">

    {% block stylesheets %}{% endblock %}
</head>
<body class="d-flex flex-column min-vh-100">

    {% include 'partials/_header.html.twig' with {theme: theme} %}

    <main class="container py-4 flex-grow-1">
        {% for message in app.flashes('success') %}
            <div class="alert alert-success alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
                {{ message|trans }}
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert"></button>
            </div>
        {% endfor %}
        {% for message in app.flashes('error') %}
            <div class="alert alert-danger alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
                {{ message|trans }}
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert"></button>
            </div>
        {% endfor %}

        {% block body %}{% endblock %}
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-body-tertiary border-top mt-auto pt-5 pb-4">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row gy-4 mb-4">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h5 class="fw-bold mb-3 d-flex align-items-center">
                        <i class="bi bi-shop text-primary fs-4 me-2"></i> Bouffay Shop
                    </h5>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0 pe-md-4" style="line-height: 1.6; max-width: 400px;">
                        La marketplace de référence pour découvrir, acheter et vendre vos produits préférés en toute sécurité.
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-md-6 text-md-end">
                    <h5 class="fw-bold mb-3">Projet Universitaire</h5>
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-md-end">
                        <div class="text-end me-3">
                            <div class="fw-semibold">Développement Web</div>
                            <div class="text-muted small">Licence 3 MIAGE</div>
                        </div>
                        <img src="https://www.univ-nantes.fr/images/logo.png" alt="Nantes Université" height="40">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <hr class="opacity-10 mb-4">
            
            <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-lg-row justify-content-between align-items-center gap-3 text-center text-lg-start">
                <div class="text-muted small">
                    &copy; {{ 'now'|date('Y') }} <span class="fw-semibold">Bouffay Shop</span>. Tous droits réservés.
                </div>
                
                <div class="text-muted text-lg-end" style="font-size: 0.70rem; max-width: 650px;">
                    <i class="bi bi-info-circle me-1"></i> Ce site est un projet strictement universitaire à but éducatif et non lucratif. Les marques, images et noms de produits affichés appartiennent à leurs ayants droit respectifs et sont utilisés uniquement à des fins d'illustration.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    {% block javascripts %}{% endblock %}
</body>
</html>
